dct_title_s: Bordentown-Trenton Delaware River Bordentown-Hutchinsons Pond Sea Level Project between Bordentown Cheesequake Creek
dct_description_sm: Area from Bordentown to Hutchinsons Pond

Map shows contour lines, monuments, triangulation, boring, and low water locations. Woods, cultivated, concrete, marsh and trees, and brush areas. Soundings for the Delaware River. The Delaware River and Crosswicks Creek, and Carlyle Creek are shown. There are two tables: 1) info about borings, 2) about triangulation and benchmarks"
